Recalls the high-level meeting of the General Assembly on the rule of law at the national and international levels, held during the high-level segment of its sixty-seventh session, and the declaration adopted at that meeting,
Resolution 67/1. takes note of the report of the Secretary-General submitted pursuant to paragraph 41 of the declaration,
A/68/213/Add.1. and requests the Sixth Committee to continue its consideration of ways and means of further developing the linkages between the rule of law and the three pillars of the United Nations;
